INCLUDE_CHILDREN

public static java.lang.String INCLUDE_CHILDREN
'include' is used to fetch associated data with Issue. It is optional. Use can specify any number of include criteria with request as comma separated values(e.g ?include=relations,journals). Possible values: children, attachments, relations, changesets and journals.
